# web-terminal-ui CSS — the REFERENCE FULL-PAGE bundle.
# What the full-page product serves (web-terminal-server, web-terminal-kiro,
# scaffold/index.html): the page kit (page.css — html/body reset + @font-face;
# full-page hosts ONLY) plus the complete tabbed component set. An EMBEDDING
# consumer must NOT serve this file's bundle — it concatenates the per-preset
# manifest matching its composition instead (MANIFEST.single / MANIFEST.touch /
# MANIFEST.tabbed), which contains no page-level rules.
# Files concatenate in declared order; the order IS the cascade.
